This is version two of fy_fireworld
===================== changes / additions - brighter - removed smoke from the floor - improved the fps - changed some textures - added lava to the fire pits - made glass over fire pits breakable - got a nave file done by chizbone - added some ambient sounds ===================== thanks to - chizbone for making the nav file - karatekafer for his awesome skybox textures - seroliser for doing the basic layout / build ===================== there may be a version three or a final version to be released yet but this could be the final
